    answer: `AI Email Response is an add-on at £${pricing.addOn.price}/month on top of the Core plan (£${pricing.tiers.core.price}/month with ${pricing.tiers.core.minutes} minutes of talk time). Setup is £${pricing.setup.price} one-time, refundable within 30 days.`
  },
  {
    question: "Can it handle bathroom layout attachments?",
    answer: "The AI notes that attachments have been received but does not analyse them. Floor plans and specifications are for you to review during follow-up."
  },
  {
    question: "How is email data protected?",
    answer: "All email data is managed under UK GDPR. Content, sender details, and attachments are encrypted and stored on UK and EU servers, shared only with you."
  }
];
