  scenario="It is 4:50pm on a Friday. An architect in Brighton emails your business address with a detailed bathroom specification for a luxury coastal apartment conversion — freestanding baths, rainfall showers, heated towel rails, underfloor heating, and floor-to-ceiling porcelain tiles. They have attached elevation drawings and want a quote by Wednesday. You are packing up from a wet room installation in Hove. Without AI Email Response, the architect sends the same specification to four other bathroom companies over the weekend. Two acknowledge within the hour and one arranges a site visit for Monday. With AI Email Response, the architect gets an acknowledgement at 4:51pm: 'Thank you for the detailed specification. We have received the drawings and will review everything on Monday morning. We will be in touch to discuss the project and arrange a site visit.' Monday morning, you open the summary and call first."
